1
00:00:02,920 --> 00:00:04,680
Here comes Thotsakan.

2
00:00:24,640 --> 00:00:25,730
Is that you, Saen?

3
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:29,840
He carries himself well, doesn't he?

4
00:00:31,680 --> 00:00:34,010
He carries himself well enough.

5
00:00:35,560 --> 00:00:37,040
He is rather small,

6
00:00:38,320 --> 00:00:40,680
but once in his dance costume

7
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:44,200
he seems scarcely inferior
to my ungrateful son.

8
00:00:47,680 --> 00:00:51,020
His skill is well worth cultivating.

9
00:00:51,440 --> 00:00:53,380
If he remains a servant,

10
00:00:54,620 --> 00:00:57,860
he will surely be punished
simply for his loyalty to his master.

11
00:00:58,640 --> 00:01:00,800
What a great shame that would be.

12
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:03,560
Do you see?

13
00:01:04,100 --> 00:01:06,240
Such is the virtue of a royal Khon dancer.

14
00:01:06,660 --> 00:01:09,800
Faithful and loyal to his master.

15
00:01:10,600 --> 00:01:11,950
Is that not so?

16
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:14,960
He is a servant.

17
00:01:15,420 --> 00:01:19,640
How could the lowborn
be equal to the nobility?

18
00:01:23,320 --> 00:01:24,960
I see the matter otherwise.

19
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:28,160
Let him be placed under
the Department of Royal Entertainments.

20
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:30,600
Let him be trained as a Phranluang student.

21
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:33,560
Let him be trained
to play a giant in the royal troupe.

22
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:36,800
At least he shall remain in your care.

23
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:39,400
He shall make no more trouble.

24
00:01:41,260 --> 00:01:43,000
I am of the same mind.

25
00:01:43,860 --> 00:01:47,380
So his skill shall serve to atone
for his wrongdoing.

26
00:01:48,380 --> 00:01:50,290
So that you need not punish him again.

27
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:54,040
Very well, then.

28
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:58,960
Since you are both in agreement,

29
00:02:00,440 --> 00:02:01,680
I shall not object.

30
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:05,920
But if he should bring me
the least disgrace…

31
00:02:06,240 --> 00:02:08,340
You need not concern yourself with that.

32
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:10,520
I shall remind him myself.

33
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:13,810
Listen, young man.

34
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:17,630
When you are
in the Department of Royal Entertainments,

35
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:21,080
do not bring shame upon your master.

36
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:25,960
Or else it shall not be
only scars upon your back,

37
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:28,020
but you shall be torn in two.

38
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:45,040
I shall bear it well in mind.

39
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:09,640
[Tanakorn Chuen-arom as Saen/Sand]

40
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:14,400
[Wacharathon Wongyai as Rak/Lucky]

41
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:18,520
[Worachai Areewong as Tan/Thank]

42
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:23,600
[Khitaphat Choothai as Chim/Charm]

43
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:27,200
[Kornkamon Supaseripap as Vila/ViVi]

44
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:31,460
[Rungtiva Sangngoen as Prink
Napat Seela as Rit/Ton]

45
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:35,040
[Chalisa Schaub as Kamala
Weeraachai Hatgovit as Phraya Banleng]

46
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:39,400
[Nithiroj Simakamtorn as Phraya Dechanarong
Rattanachai Phakdirat as Khon Master]

47
00:04:29,280 --> 00:04:30,280
Saen,

48
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:31,800
are you still awake?

49
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:36,680
Do not move.

50
00:04:42,180 --> 00:04:43,640
Your wounds will reopen.

51
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:48,280
I came to wipe you down
with a damp cloth.

52
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:34,560
These wounds...

53
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:41,400
I inflicted them upon you.

54
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:46,520
It is nothing, Master.

55
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:04,200
I am your master.

56
00:06:07,060 --> 00:06:08,340
You are my servant.

57
00:06:12,340 --> 00:06:13,800
This is not proper, is it?

58
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:24,220
Who said I am a mere servant?

59
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:30,320
You are quite mischievous, Saen.

60
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:35,020
And so stubborn.

61
00:06:43,700 --> 00:06:45,440
So alluring.

62
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:49,750
And...

63
00:06:54,460 --> 00:06:55,540
so dear.

64
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:04,480
Yes...

65
00:07:05,260 --> 00:07:06,260
dear.

66
00:07:21,660 --> 00:07:23,880
And you are my dearest.

67
00:07:53,980 --> 00:07:59,640
♫Yet night blooms perfume the dark,♫

68
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:03,910
♫Long is the night♫

69
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:10,280
♫Bright is our love,♫

70
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:16,000
♫Behind the world's dark veil♫

71
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:23,880
♫I need not praise,♫

72
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:29,120
♫Nor flowery flattery,♫

73
00:08:30,220 --> 00:08:33,030
♫From any soul but you♫

74
00:08:33,860 --> 00:08:35,180
Alright, everyone.

75
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,940
Let's start by warming up our legs today.

76
00:08:37,460 --> 00:08:38,380
Keep your arms straight.

77
00:08:39,060 --> 00:08:40,500
Bend your knees like this.

78
00:08:41,180 --> 00:08:42,370
Heels together.

79
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,820
Start with your left leg.

80
00:08:45,220 --> 00:08:46,560
Lift your knee.

81
00:08:47,740 --> 00:08:48,700
Like this.

82
00:08:49,020 --> 00:08:50,340
Then your right leg.

83
00:08:51,420 --> 00:08:52,700
Repeat on the spot.

84
00:08:53,100 --> 00:08:54,100
Now, left leg.

85
00:08:54,740 --> 00:08:55,580
One.

86
00:08:56,980 --> 00:08:57,860
Two.

87
00:08:58,960 --> 00:08:59,860
Three.

88
00:09:00,900 --> 00:09:01,780
Four.

89
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:03,620
Five.

90
00:09:07,060 --> 00:09:10,060
Next, take small steps in place.

91
00:09:10,560 --> 00:09:11,380
Start!

92
00:09:12,500 --> 00:09:13,340
One.

93
00:09:13,900 --> 00:09:14,780
Two.

94
00:09:15,300 --> 00:09:16,180
Three.

95
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:17,540
Four.

96
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:18,860
Five.

97
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:20,380
Okay.

98
00:09:21,420 --> 00:09:22,700
That's all for today.

99
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:24,280
You can rest now.

100
00:09:26,020 --> 00:09:27,260
Let's sit down.

101
00:09:29,180 --> 00:09:30,580
- I'm sore.
- I'm beat.

102
00:09:31,940 --> 00:09:33,140
My legs are killing me.

103
00:09:33,180 --> 00:09:34,980
- I'm hungry.
- Me too.

104
00:09:35,020 --> 00:09:36,020
Wanna get shabu-shabu?

105
00:09:36,060 --> 00:09:37,280
- Count me in.
- I'm so tired.

106
00:09:37,310 --> 00:09:39,460
- Was that a voice crack?
- Of course I'm tired.

107
00:09:42,260 --> 00:09:43,460
Which broth do you want?

108
00:09:43,940 --> 00:09:45,140
- Tom yum.
- Sure.

109
00:09:45,180 --> 00:09:46,770
- Right.
- For the broth...

110
00:09:47,150 --> 00:09:48,610
You guys think that's fair?

111
00:09:48,740 --> 00:09:49,490
Huh?

112
00:09:50,420 --> 00:09:52,100
Having a dictator as your leader...

113
00:09:52,380 --> 00:09:53,620
Is that what you want?

114
00:09:57,100 --> 00:09:58,420
Just think about it for a minute.

115
00:09:58,660 --> 00:10:01,020
In this room,
who gets to make the decisions?

116
00:10:04,820 --> 00:10:05,820
Nobody.

117
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:09,300
Everything has to be approved
by the club president.

118
00:10:11,700 --> 00:10:14,340
Sida has to be that way.
Thotsakan has to be this way.

119
00:10:15,900 --> 00:10:17,300
He's not creative.

120
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:19,520
This club

121
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:22,260
isn't here to preserve our culture.

122
00:10:23,140 --> 00:10:24,900
It's here to monopolize it!

123
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:30,900
That guy, Lucky, doesn't treasure Khon.

124
00:10:31,540 --> 00:10:33,700
He treasures the power
that comes with the mask.

125
00:10:39,500 --> 00:10:41,780
You still want a dictator like him
as your leader?

126
00:10:45,380 --> 00:10:47,660
If you want a creative leader,

127
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:49,620
stand up!

128
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,140
Come on.

129
00:10:55,660 --> 00:10:57,220
Yeah! That's my guy!

130
00:10:57,740 --> 00:10:59,860
Guys, our table's ready.

131
00:11:00,180 --> 00:11:01,100
What?

132
00:11:01,130 --> 00:11:02,300
- Really?
- Nice!

133
00:11:02,340 --> 00:11:03,500
Let's go!

134
00:11:03,540 --> 00:11:05,020
- Let's get the black broth.
- Lucky,

135
00:11:05,060 --> 00:11:06,620
you're coming with us, yeah?

136
00:11:06,740 --> 00:11:07,940
- Hurry!
- Let's go!

137
00:11:08,300 --> 00:11:09,300
Come on!

138
00:11:13,340 --> 00:11:16,380
And why do I have to be
the one caught in the crossfire?

139
00:11:16,700 --> 00:11:18,740
Why does this always happen to me?

140
00:11:21,860 --> 00:11:22,860
Why are you laughing?

141
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:26,380
I told you.

142
00:11:26,940 --> 00:11:28,540
Khon is Khon.

143
00:11:29,180 --> 00:11:30,800
Any deviation from it...

144
00:11:31,340 --> 00:11:32,980
is not Khon.

145
00:11:44,820 --> 00:11:47,020
And so begins
the first night of the Khon war.

146
00:11:47,060 --> 00:11:50,170
The reformers have not yet won,
and the conservatives have not yet lost.

147
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:55,180
But the war isn't over.
Don't count the bodies just yet.

148
00:12:27,880 --> 00:12:28,580
Hey.

149
00:12:29,220 --> 00:12:31,060
You don't usually practice at this hour.

150
00:12:31,860 --> 00:12:33,540
How are you allowed to be here?

151
00:12:40,780 --> 00:12:41,500
Wait...

152
00:12:42,220 --> 00:12:43,700
That's a Sida movement.

153
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,380
Aren't you supposed to be Phra Lak?

154
00:12:46,020 --> 00:12:47,590
- Why are you...
- Yeah.

155
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,210
So what?

156
00:12:50,800 --> 00:12:51,900
You have a problem?

157
00:12:56,300 --> 00:12:57,900
You want to be Sida?

158
00:12:59,420 --> 00:13:01,300
But Lucky cast you as Phra Lak?

159
00:13:03,540 --> 00:13:05,980
Yes. He said

160
00:13:06,780 --> 00:13:08,620
Sida has to be a woman.

161
00:13:09,140 --> 00:13:10,540
And someone got the role.

162
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:12,300
What?

163
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,260
That's not fair.

164
00:13:19,380 --> 00:13:22,500
I told you, he's a dictator.

165
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:24,800
You're such a good dancer,

166
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:26,990
yet you still lost to so-called traditions.

167
00:13:27,400 --> 00:13:29,180
That's ridiculous.

168
00:13:31,420 --> 00:13:34,420
Art is where creative people
show their talents.

169
00:13:35,640 --> 00:13:37,500
It isn't a place for rule followers.

170
00:13:42,060 --> 00:13:45,700
Well, when it comes to Khon,
it has to be that way.

171
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:53,870
Well...

172
00:13:55,160 --> 00:13:56,340
Are you...

173
00:13:57,300 --> 00:13:58,140
No offense, but...

174
00:13:58,860 --> 00:14:00,420
are you gay?

175
00:14:00,940 --> 00:14:01,860
What?!

176
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,660
Are you crazy?

177
00:14:03,700 --> 00:14:05,020
I'm a straight man.

178
00:14:05,220 --> 00:14:07,540
I just like cross-dressing.

179
00:14:08,020 --> 00:14:09,380
Okay.

180
00:14:09,660 --> 00:14:10,980
What the hell...

181
00:14:11,020 --> 00:14:12,180
How is that weird?

182
00:14:12,340 --> 00:14:15,020
You're a human,
yet you want to play a giant.

183
00:14:21,730 --> 00:14:24,450
I know a way to help you become Sida.

184
00:14:27,580 --> 00:14:28,580
How?

185
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:33,140
Pick me for club president.

186
00:14:35,380 --> 00:14:36,230
What?

187
00:14:41,620 --> 00:14:43,260
You still haven't given up?

188
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:44,860
It's not happening.

189
00:14:46,140 --> 00:14:50,260
Lucky is the grandson of a national artist.

190
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:54,140
And he founded this club.

191
00:14:54,780 --> 00:14:57,580
How can you take his place?

192
00:14:58,380 --> 00:14:59,740
That's not the point.

193
00:15:01,060 --> 00:15:04,460
If we gather all the like-minded people,

194
00:15:04,500 --> 00:15:06,540
we can bring him down.

195
00:15:11,820 --> 00:15:12,700
Okay.

196
00:15:14,360 --> 00:15:15,220
Deal.

197
00:15:17,260 --> 00:15:19,860
What's the plan, then?

198
00:15:20,060 --> 00:15:21,380
How are you gonna convince the others?

199
00:15:22,280 --> 00:15:23,220
Well...

200
00:15:23,700 --> 00:15:24,800
I don't have anything yet.

201
00:15:25,300 --> 00:15:26,180
Get lost.

202
00:15:26,660 --> 00:15:28,220
I thought you had a plan.

203
00:15:30,500 --> 00:15:31,900
Why don't you help me?

204
00:15:34,100 --> 00:15:37,340
Khon is usually hard to understand, right?

205
00:15:38,540 --> 00:15:40,380
Then let's make it easier to understand.

206
00:15:40,980 --> 00:15:43,700
I'm thinking... we add CGI.

207
00:15:43,740 --> 00:15:45,740
Rama shoots a laser at Thotsakan.

208
00:15:46,940 --> 00:15:48,180
Sh*t!

209
00:15:49,140 --> 00:15:50,380
That's a good idea.

210
00:15:50,980 --> 00:15:54,100
We could shoot it vertically

211
00:15:54,140 --> 00:15:55,820
and post it on TikTok.

212
00:15:56,140 --> 00:15:57,580
I guarantee it'll hit 100 million views.

213
00:15:58,220 --> 00:15:59,460
- You in?
- You're a genius...

214
00:15:59,740 --> 00:16:00,700
Right?

215
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:02,300
You're a genius!

216
00:16:02,340 --> 00:16:03,740
Let's do it now!

217
00:16:04,540 --> 00:16:05,780
Are you insane?

218
00:16:06,100 --> 00:16:07,620
We don't have anything ready.

219
00:16:08,580 --> 00:16:09,580
You're right...

220
00:16:11,180 --> 00:16:12,200
Let's meet tomorrow, then.

221
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:13,380
I'll bring some stuff.

222
00:16:14,740 --> 00:16:16,540
Okay. Why not?

223
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:24,740
Okay...

224
00:16:25,100 --> 00:16:26,100
I'm recording now.

225
00:16:26,900 --> 00:16:27,700
Ready?

226
00:16:28,520 --> 00:16:31,260
Three, two, one, go!

227
00:16:43,160 --> 00:16:44,420
You sure about this?

228
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:46,340
Why? What's wrong?

229
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:48,820
Are you pulling a Lucky on me again?

230
00:16:50,140 --> 00:16:51,140
No.

231
00:16:51,500 --> 00:16:53,030
You look so cool!

232
00:16:53,520 --> 00:16:54,520
- Okay.
- How about this?

233
00:16:55,160 --> 00:16:56,580
Let's go through every move, okay?

234
00:16:56,620 --> 00:16:57,620
Sure thing.

235
00:17:03,160 --> 00:17:05,980
My dear Sida, don't leave me!

236
00:17:08,580 --> 00:17:10,420
What are you on about, Edgy?

237
00:17:10,880 --> 00:17:11,580
Huh?

238
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:13,300
What's wrong?

239
00:17:14,060 --> 00:17:15,380
Wrong scene.

240
00:17:15,420 --> 00:17:16,940
This is where I get captured.

241
00:17:19,300 --> 00:17:20,140
Really?

242
00:17:20,180 --> 00:17:21,100
Really.

243
00:17:21,540 --> 00:17:23,260
- But it was so good.
- Nonsense.

244
00:17:23,300 --> 00:17:25,220
Do it again.
That wasn't good. Are you kidding?

245
00:17:26,100 --> 00:17:27,900
You sure you know Ramakien?

246
00:17:28,560 --> 00:17:30,820
- Let's start over.
- Alright.

247
00:17:31,300 --> 00:17:32,740
I like the last clip. Shame.

248
00:17:32,780 --> 00:17:34,220
Okay. Starting over.

249
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:44,900
Activating Hell Mode Thotsakan!

250
00:17:45,300 --> 00:17:47,100
Holy sh*t!

251
00:17:48,140 --> 00:17:49,420
That's so seamless!

252
00:17:49,460 --> 00:17:50,940
Cheap explosion sound effects.

253
00:17:54,500 --> 00:17:55,500
Good sh*t.

254
00:17:55,780 --> 00:18:00,580
[Activating Hell Mode Thotsakan]

255
00:18:03,860 --> 00:18:06,100
This will let me dominate the world!

256
00:18:11,140 --> 00:18:12,140
You like to dominate, huh?

257
00:18:14,180 --> 00:18:15,260
What are you talking about?

258
00:18:16,540 --> 00:18:17,420
Hey, look!

259
00:18:17,700 --> 00:18:18,540
What is it?

260
00:18:19,820 --> 00:18:20,820
We've got views.

261
00:18:22,060 --> 00:18:23,340
D*mn!

262
00:18:23,540 --> 00:18:25,060
Whoa, that was fast.

263
00:18:25,260 --> 00:18:26,020
Oh!

264
00:18:27,260 --> 00:18:29,100
We have comments.

265
00:18:29,340 --> 00:18:30,500
Ten... Twenty.

266
00:18:30,540 --> 00:18:31,860
No way!

267
00:18:31,900 --> 00:18:33,060
- Holy sh*t!
- Holy sh*t!

268
00:18:33,600 --> 00:18:34,980
We're going to make it.

269
00:18:38,980 --> 00:18:40,700
How are you guys today?

270
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:42,780
I'm fine. Why?

271
00:18:42,820 --> 00:18:44,900
Check this sh*t out first.

272
00:18:44,940 --> 00:18:46,740
Oh, sh*t. Your pants.

273
00:18:47,340 --> 00:18:49,260
I'm no better. Look.

274
00:18:49,300 --> 00:18:50,540
My pants ripped.

275
00:18:51,340 --> 00:18:53,140
We're all messed up.

276
00:18:53,180 --> 00:18:54,180
For real.

277
00:18:54,220 --> 00:18:56,020
Hey, guys. Look at this.

278
00:18:56,060 --> 00:18:59,060
My vertical Khon video
got 20,000 views overnight.

279
00:18:59,380 --> 00:19:00,380
Really?

280
00:19:00,420 --> 00:19:01,980
Last night it had only a few hundred views.

281
00:19:02,220 --> 00:19:04,380
I told you.
Look at all the comments.

282
00:19:04,420 --> 00:19:06,460
D*mn. It went viral.

283
00:19:06,620 --> 00:19:07,820
Look how it's blowing up.

284
00:19:07,860 --> 00:19:10,020
I think we should make a sequel.

285
00:19:10,500 --> 00:19:11,500
Are you in?

286
00:19:12,060 --> 00:19:13,480
Come on, it's a great idea.

287
00:19:14,220 --> 00:19:15,060
Alright.

288
00:19:15,500 --> 00:19:17,860
Hey, why the long face?

289
00:19:18,100 --> 00:19:19,460
Are you sulking, babe?

290
00:19:21,300 --> 00:19:22,610
You want to join us?

291
00:19:26,100 --> 00:19:27,860
I don't want to join your circus.

292
00:19:29,560 --> 00:19:30,900
What circus?

293
00:19:31,700 --> 00:19:34,380
Does your Khon
ever get as many views as mine?

294
00:19:35,660 --> 00:19:37,300
You call that Khon?

295
00:19:38,020 --> 00:19:39,540
It's just a ground-floor circus show.

296
00:19:39,580 --> 00:19:41,260
Hey, you're going too far.

297
00:19:41,300 --> 00:19:42,540
A so-called rooftop-level Khon dancer.

298
00:19:43,140 --> 00:19:44,500
'National Artist.'

299
00:19:44,940 --> 00:19:46,180
If you're as good as you say,

300
00:19:46,640 --> 00:19:48,220
get as many views as I did.

301
00:19:50,780 --> 00:19:52,420
Why do I have to compete with you?

302
00:19:53,320 --> 00:19:55,170
You're just some edgy kid,

303
00:19:55,460 --> 00:19:56,460
desperate for fame

304
00:19:57,020 --> 00:19:58,620
and completely clueless.

305
00:19:59,060 --> 00:20:00,060
So what?

306
00:20:00,500 --> 00:20:02,220
Art can cross borders.

307
00:20:03,120 --> 00:20:04,500
Japanese art is great.

308
00:20:04,540 --> 00:20:05,660
Thai art is amazing.

309
00:20:05,900 --> 00:20:07,260
I just combined the two.

310
00:20:07,700 --> 00:20:08,700
Where did I go wrong?

311
00:20:09,740 --> 00:20:11,260
It's wrong because you show no respect.

312
00:20:12,140 --> 00:20:13,140
What about you?

313
00:20:13,980 --> 00:20:16,720
Have you ever respected
anyone but yourself?

314
00:20:17,500 --> 00:20:19,260
Acting like you own Khon.

315
00:20:19,740 --> 00:20:21,460
I love my Khon, too.

316
00:20:23,340 --> 00:20:24,740
You call that love?

317
00:20:25,660 --> 00:20:27,860
Turning Khon into a joke?

318
00:20:31,260 --> 00:20:32,140
Yes.

319
00:20:33,300 --> 00:20:34,860
At least people watch my Khon.

320
00:20:35,270 --> 00:20:36,460
Not like yours.

321
00:20:36,780 --> 00:20:38,260
You're dancing for empty walls.

322
00:20:54,380 --> 00:20:55,100
What?

323
00:20:55,860 --> 00:20:57,100
Who recorded this?

324
00:20:57,140 --> 00:20:58,140
I don't know.

325
00:20:58,180 --> 00:20:59,700
I just watched it with you.

326
00:21:01,220 --> 00:21:02,500
You call that love?

327
00:21:03,500 --> 00:21:05,740
Turning Khon into a joke?

328
00:21:07,220 --> 00:21:07,980
Yes.

329
00:21:09,180 --> 00:21:10,940
At least people watch my Khon.

330
00:21:11,220 --> 00:21:12,220
Not like yours.

331
00:21:12,620 --> 00:21:14,180
You're dancing for empty walls.

332
00:21:25,020 --> 00:21:29,420
Sand and Lucky,
please go see the principal now.

333
00:21:45,620 --> 00:21:49,620
Do you know
what's going on at our school right now?

334
00:21:57,580 --> 00:21:59,180
You're just some edgy kid,

335
00:21:59,620 --> 00:22:00,620
desperate for fame

336
00:22:01,200 --> 00:22:02,700
and completely clueless.

337
00:22:03,340 --> 00:22:04,340
So what?

338
00:22:11,300 --> 00:22:13,700
I allowed you to run this club

339
00:22:15,020 --> 00:22:17,040
because I want you
to carry on our traditions,

340
00:22:17,980 --> 00:22:21,420
not damage the school's reputation.

341
00:22:22,560 --> 00:22:23,780
I am sorry.

342
00:22:24,620 --> 00:22:26,780
I just don't want Khon to be ridiculed.

343
00:22:27,340 --> 00:22:29,460
And you do that
by looking down on people?

344
00:22:31,820 --> 00:22:33,660
I just want Khon to be more accessible.

345
00:22:34,540 --> 00:22:37,300
By not listening to others' advice?

346
00:22:40,020 --> 00:22:40,900
Well then.

347
00:22:42,440 --> 00:22:44,500
I understand your intentions are good.

348
00:22:44,820 --> 00:22:47,060
But if you don't listen to each other,

349
00:22:47,520 --> 00:22:48,700
I don't think this will work out.

350
00:22:49,820 --> 00:22:51,200
From now on,

351
00:22:52,620 --> 00:22:55,540
all club activities will be suspended.

352
00:22:57,340 --> 00:22:59,300
You will have to prove

353
00:22:59,580 --> 00:23:02,060
that you can work together

354
00:23:03,580 --> 00:23:06,900
and produce work
that reflects well on the school

355
00:23:07,100 --> 00:23:08,900
to make up for this.

356
00:23:11,400 --> 00:23:12,980
But if you fail,

357
00:23:14,060 --> 00:23:16,260
I will disband your club.
